Hi, How does staking happen in the Bittensor

Stake accumulates on the miners. If they set weights these are used to validate the miners proportional to their stake holdings. More stake more power to validate and also accumulate bonds. Bonds are-attached to the miners themselves owned by the validators who bought them. Buying occurs automatically based on the weights you set. validators accrue part of the inflation which goes to the miners in the system whom they have bought bonds in.
To stake and unstake Tao use the cli
btcli unstake
And
btcli stake
To set weights run either of the miner or validator classes. Do not run the server class.
